        {
            "title": "新世界總債務1461億　鄭家純：時勢不由人，然變局如潮，何以舟楫？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"新世界鄭家純。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Fv2ltonKG8_cTKz8R1d8Cw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/sl/am730_578/f381935248229f67dc65f821e3d54749\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">新世界鄭家純。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:新世界;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/新世界\">新世界</a>發展(017)今日公布截至6月底止年度業績，總債務約為1,461億港元(下同)，於2025財年減少約57億元；凈債務約為1,201億元，同期</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>減少約35億元；短期債務約為66億元，減少約350億港元；淨負債比率增5.6%至58.1%。</span></span></span></span></span>截至6月30日，新世界已完成約882億元的貸款再融資及協調工作。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"新世界。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"651\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/n_FDiqUAr26z9ex5nXx.dA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/sl/am730_578/d8ee5b1b2bd68df50f7d7cbdf1e4252b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">新世界。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">期內，<span><span><span><span><span>可動用資金共約450億元，包括現金及銀行結餘約259億元及可動用的銀行貸款約192億元，</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>董事會決議不派發末期股息。</span></span></span></span></span></p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cfdadeee-c5de-3934-b0df-4c56ae1574c2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">持續經營業務收入按年下降23%至276.81億元，集團表示主要由於多個舊有項目接近完工，導致來自建築業務的收入減少等所致。核心經營溢利按年減少12.8%至60.17億元；受一次性撥備及虧損影響，去年度股東應佔虧損163.02億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>新世界主席鄭家純在業績報告中表示：「</span></span></span></span></span>過去一年，市場環境複雜多變，挑 戰層出不窮」，又說：<span><span><span><span><span>「時勢不由人，然變局如潮，何以舟楫？」他認為</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>面對複雜多變的挑戰，韌性成為新世界抵禦風浪、穿越週期的堅實根基，「我們以戰略定力錨定方向，於壓力中沉潛蓄勢，在衝擊下柔韌破局，始終葆有與時俱進的活力」。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>資料來源：<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:新世界公告;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2025/0926/2025092600762_c.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新世界公告</a></span></span></span></span></span></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/新世界總債務1461億-鄭家純-時勢不由人-然變局如潮-何以舟楫-/603411?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/新世界總債務1461億-鄭家純-時勢不由人-然變局如潮-何以舟楫-/603411?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/新世界總債務1461億-鄭家純-時勢不由人-然變局如潮-何以舟楫-/603411?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%B8%BD%E5%82%B5%E5%8B%991461%E5%84%84-%E9%84%AD%E5%AE%B6%E7%B4%94-%E6%99%82%E5%8B%A2%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%BA-%E7%84%B6%E8%AE%8A%E5%B1%80%E5%A6%82%E6%BD%AE-%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E8%88%9F%E6%A5%AB-091111701.html",
